<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>负载均衡 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E8%B4%9F%E8%BD%BD%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1/</link><description>负载均衡 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E8%B4%9F%E8%BD%BD%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>DNS解析与CDN</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/dns%E4%B8%8Ecdn/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/dns%E4%B8%8Ecdn/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="dns解析与cdn">DNS解析与CDN</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：DNS通过分布式层级系统将域名解析为IP地址，CDN利用DNS的智能调度和边缘节点缓存，将内容分发到离用户最近的节点，二者结合是互联网性能优化的基础设施。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="dns通过分布式层级数据库实现域名到ip的映射cdn在此基础上叠加边缘缓存和智能调度">DNS通过分布式层级数据库实现域名到IP的映射，CDN在此基础上叠加边缘缓存和智能调度</h2>
<h3 id="dns域名空间树状层级结构">DNS域名空间：树状层级结构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">                    根域名服务器 (.)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ┌────────────────────┼────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │                    │                    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   com                  org                  cn
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │                    │                    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> example              wikipedia            baidu
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │                    │                    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   www                 www                  www
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  记录: A 93.184.216.34
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        CNAME example.cdn.com</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>层级</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>示例</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>根域名（Root）</td>
          <td>最顶层，全球13组（字母A-M）</td>
          <td><code>.</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>顶级域（TLD）</td>
          <td>通用（gTLD）或国家/地区（ccTLD）</td>
          <td><code>.com</code> <code>.org</code> <code>.cn</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>二级域</td>
          <td>注册购买的主体域名</td>
          <td><code>example.com</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>子域</td>
          <td>二级域下的扩展</td>
          <td><code>www.example.com</code> <code>api.example.com</code></td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="dns解析流程从递归查询到本地缓存">DNS解析流程：从递归查询到本地缓存</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">用户输入 www.example.com
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 浏览器缓存 → 检查是否最近解析过
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 操作系统缓存 (/etc/hosts, DNS Client Service)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 本地DNS服务器（ISP或公共DNS如8.8.8.8）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   └── 递归查询开始 ──────────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 本地DNS → 根域名服务器（.）                 │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ← 返回 com 的NS记录                        │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">5. 本地DNS → com 顶级域服务器                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ← 返回 example.com 的NS记录                │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">6. 本地DNS → example.com 权威DNS服务器         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ← 返回 www.example.com 的A记录: 93.184.216.34│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">7. 本地DNS缓存结果，返回给用户 ────────────────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">总耗时：通常 20-120ms（取决于缓存命中率）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>DNS记录类型</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Dubbo RPC框架</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/dubbo/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/dubbo/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="dubbo-rpc框架">Dubbo RPC框架</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Dubbo通过注册中心实现服务自动发现，通过代理模式屏蔽远程调用细节，通过集群策略处理容错和负载均衡，是Java生态中成熟的RPC解决方案。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="dubbo通过注册中心解耦服务提供者与消费者通过代理和协议层屏蔽远程调用差异通过集群策略实现容错和负载均衡">Dubbo通过注册中心解耦服务提供者与消费者，通过代理和协议层屏蔽远程调用差异，通过集群策略实现容错和负载均衡</h2>
<h3 id="核心架构provider-consumer-registry-monitor">核心架构：Provider-Consumer-Registry-Monitor</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌─────────────┐         注册/发现          ┌─────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   Provider   │ ───────────────────────→ │   Registry   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  (服务提供者) │ ←─────────────────────── │  (注册中心)   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└──────┬──────┘      服务地址列表           └──────┬──────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │                                         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │           RPC调用（Netty/HTTP）          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │ ←─────────────────────────────────────→ │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │                                         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌──────┴──────┐                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   Consumer   │                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  (服务消费者) │                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└─────────────┘                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                                 │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌─────────────┐                                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   Monitor    │ ←───────────────────────────────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  (监控中心)   │        调用统计上报
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└─────────────┘</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>核心角色</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>网关架构</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E7%BD%91%E5%85%B3%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E7%BD%91%E5%85%B3%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="网关架构">网关架构</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：生产环境的网关通常采用LBS云网关、Nginx分发网关、业务网关三层架构，每层负责不同粒度的流量管理，共同实现高可用、高性能、安全的流量入口。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="三层网关架构分层处理流量从外到内职责逐步聚焦">三层网关架构分层处理流量，从外到内职责逐步聚焦</h2>
<h3 id="三层网关职责划分">三层网关职责划分</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">用户请求
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">LBS云网关（第一层）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 全局负载均衡（DNS/GSLB）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - DDoS防护
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - SSL卸载
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 边缘缓存（CDN）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Nginx分发网关（第二层）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 七层负载均衡
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 静态资源服务
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 限流（连接数/速率）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 灰度发布
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">业务网关（第三层）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 鉴权认证
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 路由转发
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - API治理
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 熔断降级
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">业务服务集群</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>层级</th>
          <th>代表产品</th>
          <th>核心能力</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>LBS</td>
          <td>阿里云SLB、AWS ALB</td>
          <td>四层负载均衡、健康检查</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Nginx</td>
          <td>OpenResty、Nginx Plus</td>
          <td>七层路由、Lua扩展</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>业务网关</td>
          <td>Spring Cloud Gateway、Kong</td>
          <td>API治理、微服务路由</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="nginx核心配置">Nginx核心配置</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-nginx">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-nginx" data-lang="nginx"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">upstream</span> <span class="s">backend</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">least_conn</span><span class="p">;</span>                    <span class="c1"># 最少连接算法
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">server</span> <span class="n">10.0.1.10</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">8080</span> <span class="s">weight=5</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">server</span> <span class="n">10.0.1.11</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">8080</span> <span class="s">weight=5</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">server</span> <span class="n">10.0.1.12</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">8080</span> <span class="s">backup</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1"># 备用节点
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">server</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">listen</span> <span class="mi">80</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">server_name</span> <span class="s">api.example.com</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">location</span> <span class="s">/</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">limit_req</span> <span class="s">zone=api_limit</span> <span class="s">burst=20</span> <span class="s">nodelay</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1"># 限流
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">proxy_pass</span> <span class="s">http://backend</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">proxy_set_header</span> <span class="s">Host</span> <span class="nv">$host</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">proxy_set_header</span> <span class="s">X-Real-IP</span> <span class="nv">$remote_addr</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">proxy_connect_timeout</span> <span class="s">5s</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">proxy_read_timeout</span> <span class="s">10s</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kn">location</span> <span class="s">/static</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">alias</span> <span class="s">/var/www/static</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kn">expires</span> <span class="s">30d</span><span class="p">;</span>               <span class="c1"># 静态缓存
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1单点网关故障">问题1：单点网关故障</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：网关未集群部署
<strong>解决</strong>：网关多实例+Keepalived VIP、云厂商负载均衡</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>